sentences: In 1995 he studied mathematics at the University of Virginia.
Van Arman founded the Jagjaguwar record label in 1996 in Charlottesville, Virginia.
In 1999, Van Arman dropped out of school, moved to Bloomington, Indiana, and became partners with Chris Swanson, and together began the Secretly Group.
Van Arman currently serves on the boards of A2IM, SoundExchange and Merlin.
